Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:28.43,Main01,ORYO,0,0,0,,Otae definitely went too far, but Mr. Kikuya is also at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:28.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに お妙も やり過ぎだけど\N菊屋の旦那も 悪いのよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:31.06,Main01,ORYO,0,0,0,,He keeps trying to turn this place into an all-you-can-grope buffet.
