Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.91,0:08:26.23,Main01,ANE (M),0,0,0,,I’ve never liked that about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:29.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これを機に\N店から追い払ってやるわ》
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:29.71,Main01,ANE (M),0,0,0,,This is the perfect chance to drive her out of the bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:31.03,Main01,OTAE,0,0,0,,Ane-chan.
