Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:51.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《油断させようったって\Nそうはいかないわ》
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:50.92,Main01,ANE (M),0,0,0,,I’m not letting you give me a false sense of security.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:54.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その勝負なんだけど…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:56.30,Main01,OTAE,0,0,0,,About our contest… I’ll forfeit.
