Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.33,0:24:19.41,Main01,,0,0,0,,Wow! A monstrous guy has moved in!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.41,0:24:21.74,Main01,,0,0,0,,“My neighbor Hedoro,” he looks so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.74,0:24:26.65,Main01,,0,0,0,,A florist by day, but he must be an alien conqueror by night!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.65,0:24:29.81,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,The next episode… “Do Cherries Come from Cherry Trees?”
